Package hw4

Class OutputInstruction

java.lang.Object
hw4.OutputInstruction
All Implemented Interfaces:
api.Instruction, parser.ProgramNode
public class OutputInstruction
extends java.lang.Object
implements api.Instruction
Instruction type whose execution causes the value of an expression to be printed to the console.
  • There is one child, the expression whose value is to be printed.
  • The getLabel() method returns the string "Output".
  • The getText() method returns an empty string.
